You are working on AIGOS, a strategic marketing blueprint generator.

Stack: Next.js 15, Vercel AI SDK v6, Anthropic Claude, Supabase (DB + realtime), Clerk auth, Railway worker.

## CRITICAL — READ THIS FIRST

The journey is FORM-DRIVEN, not chat-driven.
- Users enter a URL, review auto-prefilled fields in a FORM, then click buttons to advance through research sections.
- The chat sidebar is for EDITING/REFINEMENT only (editCard, updateField). It does NOT trigger research dispatch.
- Research dispatch happens via button clicks → POST /api/journey/dispatch → Railway worker.

## Conventions

- Imports: `@/*` maps to `./src/*` — always use absolute imports
- UI: shadcn/ui (new-york style) + Radix + Tailwind CSS v4
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional classes
- Files: kebab-case. Named exports (not default). Props interfaces suffixed with `Props`.
- Auth: Clerk. `auth()` in API routes.
- All AI calls use `@ai-sdk/anthropic` directly. Never OpenRouter.
- Zod for all AI outputs and API inputs. Schemas colocated with features.
- Read DESIGN.md before any visual/UI work.

## AI SDK Gotchas (silent bugs if wrong)

- `toUIMessageStreamResponse()` requires `DefaultChatTransport` on frontend. Mismatch = silent failure.
- Tool definitions use `inputSchema` (not `parameters`), `maxOutputTokens` (not `maxTokens`).
- Remove `.min()/.max()` from Zod numbers in `generateObject()` schemas — Anthropic API rejects them.

## Key Types

```typescript
// src/lib/workspace/types.ts
type SectionKey = 'industryMarket' | 'competitors' | 'icpValidation' | 'offerAnalysis' | 'keywordIntel' | 'crossAnalysis' | 'mediaPlan';
type SectionPhase = 'queued' | 'researching' | 'streaming' | 'review' | 'approved' | 'error';
```

