## Critical Gotchas

- `id` vs `run_id`: Frontend passes `run_id`. Query with `.eq('run_id', id)`.
- Railway worker (research-worker/) cannot import from src/lib/. Separate boundary.
- Pre-existing TS errors in openrouter tests and chat blueprint tests — ignore them.
